            <marker role="blank-line"></marker>
            <marker role="blank-line"></marker>
        </enactingFormula><commencementNote>[30 November 1990]</commencementNote><sourceNote>(Format changes—<ref href="hk/2019/er6">E.R. 6 of 2019</ref>)</sourceNote><section id="ID_1438403055912_001" name="s1" reason="inEffect" role="paragraph" startPeriod="2019-12-12" status="operational" temporalId="s1"><num value="1">1.</num><content>The water quality objectives set out in column 1 of the <ref>Schedule</ref> are established for those parts of the Deep Bay Water Control Zone set opposite those water quality objectives in column 2.</content></section><section id="ID_1438403055912_003" name="s2" reason="inEffect" role="paragraph" startPeriod="2024-08-18" status="operational" temporalId="s2"><num value="2"><inline class="not_bold">2.</inline></num><leadIn>In this Statement—
            <sourceNote>(<ref href="hk/2019/er6">E.R. 6 of
            2019</ref>)</sourceNote></leadIn><def name="BeasSubzone"><term>Beas
                Subzone</term>
                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">雙魚分區</term>) means the area delineated as such on maps
            DBWCZ 1, DBWCZ 2, DBWCZ 4 and DBWCZ 5;</def><def name="GangesSubzone"><term>Ganges
                Subzone</term>
                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">平原分區</term>) means the area delineated as such on map
            DBWCZ 2;</def><def name="IndusSubzone"><term>Indus
                Subzone</term>
                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">梧桐分區</term>) means the area delineated as such on maps
            DBWCZ 1 and DBWCZ 2;</def><def name="InnerMarineSubzone"><term>Inner
                Marine
            Subzone</term>
                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">內海分區</term>) means
            the sea within the
            boundary of Hong
            Kong
            to the north and east of the Mariculture Subzone;
            <sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/2024/21">21 of 2024 s.
            78</ref>)</sourceNote></def><def name="MapDBWCZ1,MapDBWCZ2,MapDBWCZ3,MapDBWCZ4,MapDBWCZ5"><term>map
                DBWCZ
            1</term>
                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">地圖 DBWCZ 1</term>),
                <term>map
                DBWCZ
            2</term>
                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">地圖 DBWCZ 2</term>),
                <term>map
                DBWCZ
            3</term>
                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">地圖 DBWCZ 3</term>),
                <term>map
                DBWCZ
            4</term>
                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">地圖 DBWCZ 4</term>) and
                <term>map
                DBWCZ
            5</term>
                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">地圖 DBWCZ 5</term>) mean a series of maps numbered as
            such and signed by the Secretary for Planning, Environment and Lands on 23 November 1990
            and deposited in the Land
                Registry;<inline class="width_3"> </inline><sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/1993/8">8 of 1993 s.
                30</ref>; <ref href="/hk/2024/21">21 of 2024 s. 78</ref>)</sourceNote></def><def name="MaricultureSubzone"><term>Mariculture
                Subzone</term>
                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">海產養殖分區</term>) means the area delineated as such on
            maps DBWCZ 1, DBWCZ 3 and DBWCZ 4;</def><def name="MarineWaters"><term>marine
                waters</term>
                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">海洋水域</term>) means all waters below the high water mark
            within the boundaries of the Deep Bay Water Control Zone;</def><def name="OuterMarineSubzone"><term>Outer
                Marine
            Subzone</term>
                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">外海分區</term>) means
            the sea within the
            boundary of Hong
            Kong
            to the north of the Secondary Contact Recreation Subzone;
            <sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/2024/21">21 of 2024 s.
            78</ref>)</sourceNote></def><def name="SecondaryContactRecreationSubzone"><term>Secondary
                Contact Recreation
            Subzone</term>
                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">次級接觸康樂活動分區</term>) means the area delineated as such on
            map DBWCZ 3;</def><def name="WaterGatheringGroundSubzones"><term>Water
                Gathering Ground
            Subzones</term>
                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">集水地區分區</term>) means the areas delineated as such on
            maps DBWCZ 2, DBWCZ 4 and DBWCZ 5;</def><def name="YuenLongKamTinLowerSubzone"><term>Yuen
                Long &amp; Kam Tin (Lower)
            Subzone</term>
                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">元朗及錦田(下)分區</term>) means the area delineated as such on
            maps DBWCZ 1 and DBWCZ 4;</def><def name="YuenLongKamTinUpperSubzone"><term>Yuen
                Long &amp; Kam Tin (Upper)
            Subzone</term>
                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">元朗及錦田(上)分區</term>) means the area delineated as such on
            maps DBWCZ 1, DBWCZ 4 and DBWCZ 5;</def><def name="YungLongBathingBeachSubzone"><term>Yung
                Long Bathing Beach
            Subzone</term>
                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">湧浪泳灘分區</term>) means the area delineated as such on map
            DBWCZ 3.</def></section><schedule id="ID_1438403055928_002" name="sch0" reason="inEffect" startPeriod="2019-12-12" status="operational" temporalId="sch0"><num value="0">Schedule</num><note class="align_right" role="crossReferences" type="inline">[<ref href="/hk/cap358R/s1">para. 1</ref>]<marker role="blank-line"></marker><marker role="blank-line"></marker></note><text>
            
            
            
            <table xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" frame="void" width="446" class="repeat_header">
                <col width="5%"></col>
                <col width="7%"></col>
